By: \'Aziz ibn Muhammad al-Nasafi
---
Self-knowledge is the shortest road to the knowledge of God. When 'Ali asked
Mohammad, ‘What am I to do that I may not waste my time?’ the Prophet
answered, ‘Learn to know thyself.’
